IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User alex.phyp@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.mbsyncgmail.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/
Inbox ~/Mail/Inbox

Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Trash"
Create Both
SyncState *
